{"data":[{"name":"77:1","price":"1. Par ceux qui sont envoyés l’un après l’autre !","arabic":"وَٱلۡمُرۡسَلَٰتِ عُرۡفٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5623,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:2","price":"2. Par les tempêtes déchaînées !","arabic":"فَٱلۡعَٰصِفَٰتِ عَصۡفٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5624,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:3","price":"3. Par ceux qui répandent et déploient,","arabic":"وَٱلنَّٰشِرَٰتِ نَشۡرٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5625,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:4","price":"4. séparent et discernent !","arabic":"فَٱلۡفَٰرِقَٰتِ فَرۡقٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5626,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:5","price":"5. Par ceux qui sèment (partout) le Rappel,","arabic":"فَٱلۡمُلۡقِيَٰتِ ذِكۡرًا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5627,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:6","price":"6. soit pour justifier soit pour avertir !","arabic":"عُذۡرًا أَوۡ نُذۡرًا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5628,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:7","price":"7. Ce qui vous est promis s’accomplira certainement.","arabic":"إِنَّمَا تُوعَدُونَ لَوَٰقِعٞ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5629,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:8","price":"8. Quand les étoiles seront éteintes,","arabic":"فَإِذَا ٱلنُّجُومُ طُمِسَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5630,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:9","price":"9. et que le ciel sera fendu,","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلسَّمَآءُ فُرِجَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5631,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:10","price":"10. et que les montagnes seront désintégrées,","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡجِبَالُ نُسِفَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5632,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:11","price":"11. et que le moment sera venu pour les Messagers de comparaître,","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلرُّسُلُ أُقِّتَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5633,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:12","price":"12. à quel jour cela est-il donc différé ?","arabic":"لِأَيِّ يَوۡمٍ أُجِّلَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5634,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:13","price":"13. Au jour de la Décision.","arabic":"لِيَوۡمِ ٱلۡفَصۡلِ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5635,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:14","price":"14. Et qui te fera jamais savoir ce qu’est le jour de la Décision ?","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا يَوۡمُ ٱلۡفَصۡلِ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5636,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:15","price":"15. Malheur, ce jour-là, aux négateurs !","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5637,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:16","price":"16. N’avons-Nous pas anéanti les (peuples) premiers ?","arabic":"أَلَمۡ نُهۡلِكِ ٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5638,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:17","price":"17. Puis n’avons-Nous pas enchaîné par les derniers ?","arabic":"ثُمَّ نُتۡبِعُهُمُ ٱلۡأٓخِرِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5639,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:18","price":"18. C’est ainsi que Nous traitons les criminels.","arabic":"كَذَٰلِكَ نَفۡعَلُ بِٱلۡمُجۡرِمِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5640,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:19","price":"19. Malheur, ce jour-là, aux négateurs !","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5641,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:20","price":"20. Ne vous avons-Nous pas créés d’un vulgaire liquide,","arabic":"أَلَمۡ نَخۡلُقكُّم مِّن مَّآءٖ مَّهِينٖ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5642,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:21","price":"21. que Nous avons établi dans un réceptacle sûr,","arabic":"فَجَعَلۡنَٰهُ فِي قَرَارٖ مَّكِينٍ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5643,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:22","price":"22. pour un délai déjà fixé ?","arabic":"إِلَىٰ قَدَرٖ مَّعۡلُومٖ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5644,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:23","price":"23. Ainsi l’avons-Nous déterminé, et nul ne le pourra mieux que Nous !","arabic":"فَقَدَرۡنَا فَنِعۡمَ ٱلۡقَٰدِرُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5645,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:24","price":"24. Malheur, ce jour-là, aux négateurs !","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5646,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:25","price":"25. N’avons-Nous pas fait de la terre un réceptacle commun","arabic":"أَلَمۡ نَجۡعَلِ ٱلۡأَرۡضَ كِفَاتًا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5647,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:26","price":"26. aux vivants et aux morts ?","arabic":"أَحۡيَآءٗ وَأَمۡوَٰتٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5648,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:27","price":"27. N’y avons-Nous pas implanté des montagnes altières ? Ne vous avons-Nous pas donné à boire une eau très douce ?","arabic":"وَجَعَلۡنَا فِيهَا رَوَٰسِيَ شَٰمِخَٰتٖ وَأَسۡقَيۡنَٰكُم مَّآءٗ فُرَاتٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5649,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:28","price":"28. Malheur, ce jour-là, aux négateurs !","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5650,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:29","price":"29. Précipitez-vous donc vers ce que vous teniez pour mensonge !","arabic":"ٱنطَلِقُوٓاْ إِلَىٰ مَا كُنتُم بِهِۦ تُكَذِّبُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5651,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:30","price":"30. Élancez-vous vers l’ombre aux trois colonnes de (la fumée de l’Enfer),","arabic":"ٱنطَلِقُوٓاْ إِلَىٰ ظِلّٖ ذِي ثَلَٰثِ شُعَبٖ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5652,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:31","price":"31. qui ne protège ni ne prémunit contre les flammes.","arabic":"لَّا ظَلِيلٖ وَلَا يُغۡنِي مِنَ ٱللَّهَبِ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5653,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:32","price":"32. Car (le Feu de la Géhenne) projette des étincelles aussi grandes que de hautes citadelles,","arabic":"إِنَّهَا تَرۡمِي بِشَرَرٖ كَٱلۡقَصۡرِ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5654,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:33","price":"33. ou semblables à des chameaux jaunes.","arabic":"كَأَنَّهُۥ جِمَٰلَتٞ صُفۡرٞ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5655,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:34","price":"34. Malheur, ce jour-là, aux négateurs !","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5656,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:35","price":"35. Ce jour-là, (les mécréants) ne pourront ni parler,","arabic":"هَٰذَا يَوۡمُ لَا يَنطِقُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5657,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:36","price":"36. ni ne seront autorisés à présenter des excuses.","arabic":"وَلَا يُؤۡذَنُ لَهُمۡ فَيَعۡتَذِرُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5658,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:37","price":"37. Malheur, ce jour-là, aux négateurs !","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5659,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:38","price":"38. Voici venu le Jour de la Décision où Nous vous réunissons avec ceux qui vous ont précédés.","arabic":"هَٰذَا يَوۡمُ ٱلۡفَصۡلِۖ جَمَعۡنَٰكُمۡ وَٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5660,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:39","price":"39. Si vous avez quelque stratagème faites-en donc usage contre Moi !","arabic":"فَإِن كَانَ لَكُمۡ كَيۡدٞ فَكِيدُونِ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5661,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:40","price":"40. Malheur, ce jour-là, aux négateurs !","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5662,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:41","price":"41. Ceux qui sont pieux seront au milieu d’ombrages et de sources (vives),","arabic":"إِنَّ ٱلۡمُتَّقِينَ فِي ظِلَٰلٖ وَعُيُونٖ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5663,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:42","price":"42. et auront les fruits qu’ils désireront.","arabic":"وَفَوَٰكِهَ مِمَّا يَشۡتَهُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5664,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:43","price":"43. « Mangez et buvez en paix pour tout ce que vous faisiez. »","arabic":"كُلُواْ وَٱشۡرَبُواْ هَنِيٓـَٔۢا بِمَا كُنتُمۡ تَعۡمَلُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5665,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:44","price":"44. C’est ainsi que Nous rétribuons les bienfaiteurs.","arabic":"إِنَّا كَذَٰلِكَ نَجۡزِي ٱلۡمُحۡسِنِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5666,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:45","price":"45. Malheur, ce jour-là, aux négateurs !","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5667,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:46","price":"46. « Mangez et jouissez pour peu de temps (ô mécréants), vous êtes certes des scélérats ! »","arabic":"كُلُواْ وَتَمَتَّعُواْ قَلِيلًا إِنَّكُم مُّجۡرِمُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5668,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:47","price":"47. Malheur, ce jour-là, aux négateurs !","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5669,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:48","price":"48. Quand il leur est dit : « Inclinez-vous (pour la Çalât) », ils ne s’inclinent pas.","arabic":"وَإِذَا قِيلَ لَهُمُ ٱرۡكَعُواْ لَا يَرۡكَعُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5670,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:49","price":"49. Malheur, ce jour-là, aux négateurs !","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5671,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:50","price":"50. En quelle parole, après celle-là, vont-ils donc croire ?","arabic":"فَبِأَيِّ حَدِيثِۭ بَعۡدَهُۥ يُؤۡمِنُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5672,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"}],"chapter":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat","Chapter Al-Mursalat","Mursalat","Surah Mursalat","Chapter Mursalat","Al Mursalat","Surah Al Mursalat","Chapter Al Mursalat","Surah 77","Chapter 77","The Emissaries","المرسلات"]}